- gEDA Internet resources

	Homepage: http://www.geda.seul.org

	Mailing lists:

   	   User List - For discussing and reporting user problems or issues

		To subscribe send an email to: majordomo@geda.seul.org  
	 	with   subscribe geda-user   in the body.

		To unsubscribe send an email to: majordomo@geda.seul.org
	 	with   unsubscribe geda-user   in the body.

		To send email to the list use the address: 
			geda-user@geda.seul.org

		You must subscribe before you can post.  You must post 
		using the subscribed e-mail address.

	   Developer List - For discussing developer issues

		To subscribe send an email to: majordomo@geda.seul.org  
	 	with   subscribe geda-dev   in the body.

		To unsubscribe send an email to: majordomo@geda.seul.org
	 	with   unsubscribe geda-dev   in the body.

		To send email to the list use the address: 
			geda-dev@geda.seul.org

		You must subscribe before you can post.  You must post 
		using the subscribed e-mail address.

		Remember, geda-dev@geda.seul.org/geda-user@geda.seul.org
	        is for the actual traffic.  For administrative commands, 
		use majordomo@geda.seul.org.

	The mailing list archive is at:

		http://www.geda.seul.org/mailinglist 

	Many thanks to the SEUL project for hosting gEDA!



